<section id="summary" class="level3">
<h3>Summary</h3>
<p>During my time with IMIS I graduated from programmer to senior programmer and had the chance to hone my skills as a software architect when I joined the architecture team. I assisted during conception and implementation of several e-business platforms for various large clients from many different industries and was also lead programmer and technical project leader for two of them. Mentoring our apprentices and junior programmers became a regular activity early on and I was involved in writing the training and learning programmes. I was also involved in the specification of use-cases. In my final function for IMIS AG I was lead programmer of a small team developing IMIS'' first dedicated e-commerce product.</p>
</section>
<section id="notable-projects" class="level3">
<h3>Notable projects</h3>
<section id="imisnext-base-shop" class="level4">
<h4>IMISNext Base Shop</h4>
<p>Consolidation of several code-bases from various customer projects into one single product. Included test-driven refactoring and working with legacy code, isolation and modularisation of existing code from previous project and implementing a REST server interface with accompanying web client.</p>
<dl>
<dt>Technologies used</dt>
<dd>Scala
</dd>
