<section id="mmshop" class="level4">
<h4>MMShop</h4>
<p>Or first e-commerce project using the Play 2.0 Framework. I was responsible for migrating large parts of the existing Play 1.2 infrastructure to Play 2.0 and Scala as well as implementing much of the future IShop/Play core library. Included implementing a web user interface using HTML, CSS and JavaScript. This project made use of external infrastructure such as LDAP for account management. A special challenge was the coordination of order processing between multiple independent SAP/R3 instances.</p>
<dl>
<dt>Technologies used</dt>
<dd>Scala
</dd>
<dd>Java
</dd>
