</dd>
<dd>GNU+Linux
</dd>
</dl>
</section>
<section id="bbshop" class="level4">
<h4>BBShop</h4>
<p>Our first e-commerce project using the Play Framework. I was involved in creating the Play infrastructure, writing the ERP connection using SAP JCO and implementing the user interface using HTML, CSS and JavaScript.</p>
<dl>
<dt>Technologies used</dt>
