<section id="ishop-architectural-evaluation" class="level4">
<h4>IShop Architectural Evaluation</h4>
<p>When it became obvious that Tapestry 4 wasn''t up to the task anymore we started evaluating several possible replacement candidates. We defined a minimal feature set and implemented two prototypes, one for each of the final candidates (Wicket and Play Framework). The final evaluation resulted in the adoption of the Play Framework for future customer projects.</p>
<dl>
<dt>Technolgies used</dt>
<dd>Play Framework 1.2
</dd>
<dd>Java
</dd>
<dd>JavaScript
</dd>
<dd>Apache Webserver
</dd>
