<section id="netmin" class="level4">
<h4>Netmin</h4>
<p>A network services account management tool with script-able plug-in interface. Allowed for the bulk creation of network services accounts such as email, personal web page and LDAP account from database records. Included script-able interface for creation and modification of service accounts. I was also tasked with mentoring an apprentice for further maintenance of the tool.</p>
