<dl>
<dt>Employer</dt>
<dd>Benmark AG, Zürich (CH)
</dd></dl><dl><dt>Job description</dt>
<dd>Software engineer / Consultant
</dd></dl><dl><dt>Responsibilities</dt>
<dd>consulting and requirements specification
